<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Instagram Token Generator</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css" />

</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
<h1>Instagram Token Generator</h1>

<form class="markdown-form" id="form" action="./submit" method="post">
    <p>Enter <a href="https://www.instagram.com/developer/clients/manage/" target="_blank">your Instagram client</a>'s <strong>client ID</strong> and <strong>client secret</strong>. On the next screen, Instagram will ask you to authorize the token.</p>
    <label>Client ID</label>
    <input type="text" name="client_id" id="client_id" value="" />
    <label>Client Secret</label>
    <input type="text" name="client_secret" id="client_secret" value="" />
    
    <label>Scopes <a href="https://medium.com/@emersonthis/instagram-on-websites-the-new-landscape-62c91d733894#37c4" target="_blank">?</a></label>
    <div class="scopes">            
        <div class="scopes__group--left scopes__group">
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="scope_basic" checked disabled /> basic</label>
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="scope_public_content" value="public_content "/> public_content</label>
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="scope_follower_list" value="follower_list" /> follower_list</label>
        </div>
        
        <div class="scopes__group--right scopes__group">
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="scope_comments" value="comments" /> comments</label>
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="scope_relationships" value="relationships" /> relationships</label>
        <label><input type="checkbox" name="scope_likes" value="likes" /> likes</label>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="submit-wrap"><input type="submit" value="Create token"></div>
</form>

<% include ../partials/footer %>

</div><!-- .container -->


</body>
</html>